cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper discusses the use of gated networks in learning relationships between input sources, activity recognition, and multi-modal representations, which are all common topics in the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses more on the technical aspects of gated networks rather than specific applications, cs.NE and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
